which he blows into...

34:22.000 --> 34:24.420
(conch blowing)

34:24.420 --> 34:28.590
...and this supposedly makes
the exact same sound of "Om"

34:28.590 --> 34:32.800
that Shiva makes
with his double‐sided drum.

34:36.220 --> 34:39.560
TSOUKALOS:
Om is a frequency

34:39.560 --> 34:42.520
of all vowels combined into one.

34:42.520 --> 34:45.360
A, E, I, O, U: Om.

34:47.480 --> 34:51.570
And some have suggested that the
Om essentially can be regarded

34:51.570 --> 34:55.030
as the frequency
of the universe.

34:55.030 --> 34:57.870
SHIMKHADA: Hinduism, Buddhism,
Jainism, Sikhism,

34:57.870 --> 35:01.120
they all use the concept of Om

35:01.120 --> 35:03.210
as an integral part
of their religion,

35:03.210 --> 35:05.630
of their understanding
of their, you know, life.

35:05.630 --> 35:09.920
Om is the sound of the universe,
the basis of everything.

35:12.880 --> 35:16.720
NARRATOR: Om is first mentioned
in the ancient Sanskrit texts

35:16.720 --> 35:21.980
called the Upanishads,
written over 3,000 years ago,

35:21.980 --> 35:27.110
which proposed that vibration,
along with ritualistic chanting,

35:27.110 --> 35:30.820
singing and prayer,
can provide a direct connection

35:30.820 --> 35:35.360
between humans
and the gods themselves.

35:35.360 --> 35:38.490
Around the world,
there is acknowledgement

35:38.490 --> 35:40.370
that things
are created by sound,

35:40.370 --> 35:42.910
and that sound
is a kind of portal,

35:42.910 --> 35:46.250
a connection point
between the seen and the unseen,

35:46.250 --> 35:49.210
the sacred and the ordinary.

35:49.210 --> 35:53.670
The Igbo people
of Nigeria in Africa

35:53.670 --> 35:58.300
believe that music is actually
the voices of their ancestors.

36:00.640 --> 36:04.350
Yakut shamans throughout
Central Asia use whistling

36:04.350 --> 36:07.190
to summon their spirit helpers

36:07.190 --> 36:10.270
when they're about to go into
trance to help their people.

36:10.270 --> 36:15.240
The Macau people
of South Asia have a poem

36:15.240 --> 36:17.990
that's linked to the idea
that music

36:17.990 --> 36:20.030
is a way to call
upon our ancestors,

36:20.030 --> 36:22.290
to sing them present with us.

36:22.290 --> 36:25.540
CHILDRESS:
This is the vibration

36:25.540 --> 36:29.460
that is inherent
in the universe,

36:29.460 --> 36:34.260
and it's something that humans
would be able to use it,

36:34.260 --> 36:37.220
with our own technology,

36:37.220 --> 36:41.850
to reconnect with the gods,
with the extraterrestrials.

36:41.850 --> 36:44.310
(chanting)

36:44.310 --> 36:46.270
NARRATOR:
Is it possible

36:46.270 --> 36:49.270
that through ancient traditions
of chanting and vocal prayer,

36:49.270 --> 36:54.820
mankind is actually connecting
to an extraterrestrial realm?

36:57.990 --> 37:02.990
And if so, might the same
be true for similar practices

37:02.990 --> 37:08.330
performed by other
major religions today?

37:08.330 --> 37:10.040
We have this in the West.

37:10.040 --> 37:14.420
Cathedrals are engineered
to affect the visitor.

37:14.420 --> 37:16.970
A seeker comes to a cathedral

37:16.970 --> 37:20.840
and the acoustics of the room
will resonate in the body.

37:20.840 --> 37:22.640
It's about sound.

37:22.640 --> 37:25.220
If you go to one of
the great cathedrals of Europe

37:25.220 --> 37:29.100
and hear a Gregorian chant
or other musical performance,

37:29.100 --> 37:31.610
it will alter
your consciousness.

37:31.610 --> 37:36.190
So, devoted to encouraging
mystical experience,

37:36.190 --> 37:38.360
connection
with the unseen world,

37:38.360 --> 37:41.740
will invent instruments, spaces,

37:41.740 --> 37:44.620
so that the human body will
resonate with certain sounds,

37:44.620 --> 37:46.660
certain music,
certain frequencies,

37:46.660 --> 37:49.960
that will put them in touch
with the unseen,

37:49.960 --> 37:55.090
whether that is the gods
or unseen wisdom.

37:55.090 --> 38:00.050
It's a way for us to get
in touch with the consciousness

38:00.050 --> 38:03.010
and the intelligence
of the extraterrestrial beings

38:03.010 --> 38:05.720
that we believe were here
in the past.

38:05.720 --> 38:07.560
They're here in the present,

38:07.560 --> 38:11.350
and they will ultimately lead us
into our future.

38:13.060 --> 38:16.270
NARRATOR: While it has
often been envisioned

38:16.270 --> 38:19.440
that mankind's first contact
with extraterrestrials

38:19.440 --> 38:21.240
would come in the form

38:21.240 --> 38:24.660
of a spaceship touching down
somewhere on Earth,

38:24.660 --> 38:30.040
could it be that contact
is already taking place,

38:30.040 --> 38:33.330
and perhaps has been going on
uninterrupted

38:33.330 --> 38:35.920
for thousands of years?

38:35.920 --> 38:39.840
Ancient astronaut theorists
say yes,

38:39.840 --> 38:42.510
and suggest the proof
of extraterrestrial contact

38:42.510 --> 38:46.930
may lie not somewhere on land,

38:46.930 --> 38:50.310
but deep beneath
the surface of the ocean.

38:56.820 --> 39:00.440
NARRATOR:
Mariana Trench, Pacific Ocean.

39:00.440 --> 39:04.700
July 13, 2015.

39:04.700 --> 39:08.620
Researchers from the
Hatfield Marine Science Center

39:08.620 --> 39:11.290
scan the deepest part
of the world's oceans

39:11.290 --> 39:15.380
with a hydrophone,
listening for whale calls.

39:15.380 --> 39:19.420
But suddenly, they pick up
something unexpected:

39:19.420 --> 39:23.130
eerie sounds
booming from the depths.

39:28.260 --> 39:30.020
These sounds
are quite interesting.

39:30.020 --> 39:32.390
They sound kind of like
whale sounds,

39:32.390 --> 39:36.520
but they can't be attached
to any known species.

39:36.520 --> 39:38.400
It's about eight miles down.

39:38.400 --> 39:44.950
It seems very technological,
but it's very mysterious.

39:44.950 --> 39:46.820
If we analyze the signal

39:46.820 --> 39:49.160
that's coming out of the depths
of the Mariana Trench,

39:49.160 --> 39:52.040
and realize that it's more
technological in nature...

39:54.370 --> 39:56.750
...could this be coming
from some base

39:56.750 --> 40:01.920
that could still be in use
by some extraterrestrial race?

40:01.920 --> 40:06.680
NARRATOR: If the strange sounds
detected at the Mariana Trench

40:06.680 --> 40:10.180
really are from
an extraterrestrial source,

40:10.180 --> 40:13.560
are they meant for us to hear?

40:13.560 --> 40:17.650
As scientists continue
to learn more

40:17.650 --> 40:21.150
about the possibilities
of acoustic technologies,

40:21.150 --> 40:25.280
and also about the vibrational
properties of the universe,

40:25.280 --> 40:28.280
are we beginning to rediscover

40:28.280 --> 40:31.660
how to detect
otherworldly communications,

40:31.660 --> 40:36.210
and possibly connect
with alien beings?

40:38.330 --> 40:40.840
When we look
at all of the evidence,

40:40.840 --> 40:43.420
we have reason to believe
that extraterrestrials

40:43.420 --> 40:46.380
are giving us clues
that help us to realize

40:46.380 --> 40:49.220
frequency plays
a much greater role

40:49.220 --> 40:53.060
in understanding matter,
energy and consciousness

40:53.060 --> 40:56.230
than we allow for in our
current scientific paradigms.

40:56.230 --> 40:58.850
TSOUKALOS:
If you have megalithic sites

40:58.850 --> 41:00.730
that feature these harmonics

41:00.730 --> 41:03.190
and they happen
to be on different continents,

41:03.190 --> 41:06.650
then one has to wonder if,
at some point,

41:06.650 --> 41:12.280
this knowledge
was given to our ancestors.

41:12.280 --> 41:16.660
I think the time has come
that we not only use our eyes

41:16.660 --> 41:18.290
to look at these things,

41:18.290 --> 41:22.040
but to also turn our ears
towards these sites.

41:22.040 --> 41:26.920
Because perhaps
the frequencies of these places

41:26.920 --> 41:31.470
may be the key to unlocking
the secrets of our past.

41:35.310 --> 41:38.480
NARRATOR: Is it possible
that extraterrestrials

41:38.480 --> 41:44.320
have used acoustics to secretly
guide mankind for millennia?

41:44.320 --> 41:48.070
Or could aliens have hidden
clues all around the world

41:48.070 --> 41:50.200
so that once discovered,

41:50.200 --> 41:54.490
we might one day be able
to initiate their return?

41:54.490 --> 41:58.000
Perhaps the truth
can only be found

41:58.000 --> 42:01.500
once we use not our eyes,
but our ears,

42:01.500 --> 42:06.960
to find the extraterrestrial
messages that surround us.
